      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "I’ve never really understood the concept of marriage, much less the idea of a wedding.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "I mean, I get it conceptually. One person to hold from this day forward, forever. But I’m not convinced the construct of marriage is the best way to assure that commitment.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "For example: Does taking your vows in front of others make people take those vows more seriously?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Our",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "recent divorce rate",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "suggests otherwise.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-0",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/fastats/marriage-divorce.htm"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "But are people who take their vows seriously more likely to stay together? Probably.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "And so, maybe, we should honor the process and not the inauguration. Make weddings",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "simple and fast and cheap and private",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "—and celebrate the big wins, the dramatic milestones, and the job well done instead.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-0",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/2019/06/27/super-easy-couples-can-officiate-their-own-wedding-dc/"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Because, marriage ain’t no movie. It takes time.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}